Package: ask
Title: Friendly Command Line Interface Tools
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Gabor Csardi [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Gabor Csardi <csardi.gabor@gmail.com>
Description: Ask questions to the user through the CLI and validate the answer.
    Several types of input are supported: yes-no question, single choice,
    multiple choice, etc.
